             x:Class="Eskisehir2.Home">
	<ContentPage.Resources>
		<ResourceDictionary>
			<x:String x:Key="eskisehir">
				Eskişehir is a city in northwestern Turkey and the capital of the Eskişehir Province. The urban population of the city is 717,135 with a metropolitan population of 826,135.The city is located on the banks of the Porsuk River, 792 m above sea level, where it overlooks the fertile Phrygian Valley.In the nearby hills one can find hot springs.
			</x:String>
		</ResourceDictionary>
	</ContentPage.Resources>

